{"tid":2273844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳無綫翻拍《十月初五的月光》 君好初哥哥將由佢哋飾演？","createTime":"2020-11-06T04:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:08:06.000Z","uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e45e18f70c75842904c938b8175157d41309b1c","tid":2273844,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"由佘詩曼及張智霖主演嘅《十月初五的月光》係唔少香港人心目中嘅經典劇集，2000年播出時主角君好（佘詩曼飾）同初哥哥（張智林飾）瞬間爆紅，而主題曲《祝君好》亦到紅到而家，一聽到「寧願沒擁抱共你可到老......」，真係咩回憶都返晒嚟。近日有傳無綫計劃翻拍《十月初五的月光》，預計下年1月開拍，而主角方面都已經有初步人選。"},{"pid":"3ddd03fb3cde09d1cd39baf1c1b1845941d483a1","tid":2273844,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:30.000Z","msg":"有指君好一角將會由擁有甜美笑容嘅17年港姐亞軍何依婷飾演，而初哥哥一角就仲未決定係陳家樂定周柏豪飾演好。至於司徒禮信（馬浚偉飾）就有傳會由何廣沛或丁子朗其中一人飾演，金勝就有由大隻仔郭子豪飾演，而君好嘅好姊妹海琳和依文將會由上屆港姐蔡嘉欣、今屆港姐冠軍謝嘉怡、亞軍陳楨怡及季軍郭柏妍等等中挑選。"},{"pid":"cb382c386a19472a364b7aa9de9f82dc49075878","tid":2273844,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"選角消息出街後，有網民認為何依婷唔太適合演君好，因為佢嘅感覺太港女，完全冇君好嘅感覺。另外，網民們亦提議咗幾位「初哥哥」嘅人選，佢哋認為「安仔」周嘉洛可塑性好高，又係最佳男配角，應該可勝任初哥哥一角，而張振朗就張智林都有幾分相似，胡鴻鈞就斯斯文文，所以佢哋兩位都啱做初哥哥。唔知大家又認為邊位演員適合做君好同初哥哥呢？"},{"pid":"a5eba8b5bcd9ca0ee19778d63bf124a769d02e5f","tid":2273844,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"老翻痴lam=初哥哥 黃浩信=司徒 肛交=君好 家燕姐=家燕姐"},{"pid":"a7f3c1004139af5fcd898222a7c805a0a4bca3d8","tid":2273844,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n何依婷靚相被登色情網 慘變「小仙女Baby」接客<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2227746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2227746</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dju1CV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dju1CV.jpg&h=97f999e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"098d22061592bb3273d8db92e28dbcf891f24251","tid":2273844,"uid":61745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"佢拍咩垃圾都一樣, wfc"},{"pid":"c14cf62ab6d4f3845a8e81a51cd244c8bface11a","tid":2273844,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"嫂 嫂不斷呼叫我<br />\n命我 扶實佢雙峰下墮"},{"pid":"1c2078fba080813644e4a28d637d3121524eda02","tid":2273844,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gn4ZEqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgn4ZEqo.jpg&h=53056661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSamSLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSamSLp.jpg&h=34bbb785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nHHMjqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnHHMjqp.jpg&h=53886bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAWUtiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAWUtiL.jpg&h=11ad2e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6M7TJR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6M7TJR5.jpg&h=4ccc98a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b77875408d146da70d1f39007584c9fbc508d6a0","tid":2273844,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"見字覺得班女嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}